metadata.name: You & I Collide
metadata.description: “You & I Collide” is a digital art piece that captures the ethereal beauty of two souls coming together in the beyond. The piece features two figures in a state of embrace, entwined in a dance of unity and harmony, celebrating the power of connection and the enduring nature of the soul. It is a reminder that even beyond the physical realm, love and connection can transcend all boundaries.
